high_descs: Turn right and walk to the table then turn left and walk to the counter.
Look up and get the mug that's on the shelf to your right.
Turn right to face the microwave.
Warm the mug in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn around and take a step then turn right to face the sink.
Put the mug in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the white table, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Open the second upper cabinet door from the left and take out the black mug, then close the cabinet.
Look down and turn right to face the microwave.
Heat up the mug in the microwave for a couple seconds then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn around and walk up to the sink.
Put the heated mug in the sink basin to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen sink to your right.
Pick up a mug from the counter.
Place the mug in the microwave and take it out.
Walk back to the kitchen sink.
Place the mug in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Warm the mug for cleaning in the sink.
